@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
    ViewData["Description"] = "About Microsoft Software Releases - Information about tracking Microsoft 365 Apps, Windows 10, and Windows 11 versions, data sources, and version tracking methodology.";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="modern-card mb-4">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="card-title">About Microsoft Software Releases</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Track Microsoft 365 Apps, Windows 10, and Windows 11 versions</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="mt-0 mb-3">Project Overview</h3>
            <p>This site provides a consolidated view of <strong>Microsoft 365 Apps</strong> versions across different update channels, as well as <strong>Windows 10</strong> and <strong>Windows 11</strong> operating system releases. It was created to help IT professionals and Microsoft 365 admins track version history, build numbers, and release schedules across all Microsoft client software.</p>
            
            <p>Microsoft Software Releases is designed to answer common questions like:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>What's the latest Current Channel version?</li>
                <li>When was the last Monthly Enterprise Channel release?</li>
                <li>Which build number corresponds to a specific version?</li>
                <li>What's the end-of-service date for a particular release?</li>
                <li>What's the latest Windows 11 or Windows 10 version available?</li>
                <li>What build number is currently deployed on Windows?</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 class="mb-3">Data Sources</h3>
            <p>All information on this site is derived exclusively from official Microsoft documentation:</p>
            <div class="row mb-3">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-1"></i>Microsoft 365 Apps</h5>
                    <ul class="small">
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/deployoffice/overview-update-channels" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Overview of update channels</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/officeupdates/update-history-microsoft365-apps-by-date" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Update history (listed by date)</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/deployoffice/update-channels-changes" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Update channel changes</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/officeupdates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Release notes</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-windows me-1"></i>Windows Operating System</h5>
                    <ul class="small">
                        <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/13853" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Windows 10 release information</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/15254" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Windows 11 release information</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/windows/release-health/release-information" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Windows release information</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/windows/deployment/update/windows-update-overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Windows Update overview</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="mb-3">Methodology</h3>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-2"></i>Release Tracking</h4>
                    <p>Version data is collected from Microsoft's official documentation and organized by product type (Microsoft 365 Apps vs Windows). Each version entry includes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Version number (e.g., 16.0.16130.20342 or 25H2)</li>
                        <li>Release date</li>
                        <li>Build information</li>
                        <li>Channel designation (for Microsoft 365) or servicing status (for Windows)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-clock-history me-2"></i>Update Frequency</h4>
                    <p>Our database is updated regularly to reflect the latest releases across all products and channels:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Microsoft 365 Apps:</strong> Multiple times per month (Current), Monthly (Monthly Enterprise), Twice yearly (Semi-Annual Enterprise)</li>
                        <li><strong>Windows 10:</strong> Monthly security updates plus periodic feature updates</li>
                        <li><strong>Windows 11:</strong> Monthly feature and quality updates</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="me-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-lightbulb fs-4"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="alert-heading">For Developers</h5>
                        <p class="mb-0">This site offers a simple API for accessing version data programmatically. See the <a href="/swagger" class="alert-link">API documentation</a> for details on how to integrate this data into your own dashboards or monitoring tools.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="modern-card mb-4">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <i class="bi bi-code-square"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="card-title">Technical Implementation</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Open-source, cloud-native approach</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>Open Source</h4>
                    <p>Microsoft Software Releases is an open-source project, with the full source code available on GitHub:</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                        <a href="https://github.com/robgrame/OfficeVersionsCore" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-modern btn-secondary">
                            <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
                            View GitHub Repository
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-3">Contributions, issues, and feature requests are welcome. Feel free to check the issues page if you want to contribute.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-cloud me-2"></i>Built With</h4>
                    <p>This site is built using modern technologies:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>ASP.NET Core (.NET 8)</li>
                        <li>Razor Pages</li>
                        <li>Azure hosting</li>
                        <li>Bootstrap 5</li>
                        <li>DataTables.js for interactive tables</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="modern-card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="card-title">Disclaimer & Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Important notices and feedback options</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h4><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>Disclaimer</h4>
                    <p>This site is <strong>not affiliated with or endorsed by Microsoft Corporation</strong>. All trademarks, service marks, and trade names referenced on this site are the property of their respective owners.</p>
                    
                    <p>The information provided is for reference purposes only and is presented "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. While every effort is made to keep the data accurate and up-to-date, you should always refer to <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/officeupdates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft's official documentation</a> for authoritative information.</p>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4"><i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Contact</h4>
                    <p>For questions, feedback, or corrections, please contact:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@office365versions.com">info@office365versions.com</a></li>
                        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/rgp-net/OfficeVersions/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Submit an issue</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border rounded bg-light h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                        <h5 class="text-center mb-3">Privacy</h5>
                        <p class="mb-4">This site uses minimal analytics to understand user patterns. No personally identifiable information is collected.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                            <a asp-page="/Privacy" class="btn-modern btn-primary">
                                <i class="bi bi-shield"></i>
                                Privacy Policy
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <p class="text-muted small mb-0">&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year Microsoft Software Releases - Built with ?? for the IT community</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

